    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Circular arrangements of natural or artificial flowers, leaves, branches, or other such materials, usually hung from doors, windows, walls, or other locations, for various purposes, such as for decoration or to honor or in commemoration of a person or event.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
